title: Chai Mai Jing Ying Tae
overview: What does a Beautiful woman, a cross dressing man and famous actor who is to judge a transgender beauty pageant have in common? They have a man who is meant to be a woman but is in reality a woman who is playing a man, who is a woman. Trust me you will get... Rin is bullied by a the gay man who spent her life savings when he finds her wallet after she helps him. So to make the money back he decides to enter a transsexual beauty pageant as he is only a cross dresser. However the contestant must be men who are now women . so he cons her into entering and Rin wins but thats because everyone thinks she is a post op woman who was a man... what will happens when they discover she is all woman and not a man. Get ready for amazing costumes, lip syncing for the best of them the gay cabaret is in town but its a woman.
